      • VideoControl

        public VideoControl(javafx.scene.media.MediaPlayer mp,
            javafx.stage.Stage s)
        Constructor for the VideoControl class. This constructor sets the default values and configuration for the fields mp, mediaView, mvPane and mediaBar. It also adds all the UI components to the Stage by accessing internal methods. See the 'See Also: ' section for more information.
        Parameters:
        mp - the MediaPlayer object associated with this VideoControl object.
        s - the Stage object associated with this VideoControl object.
        See Also:
        addLoopCheckbox(), addLoopLabel(), addPlayButton(), addSpacer(), addTimeLabel(), addTimeSlider(), addVolumeLabel(), addVolumeSlider()

        protected javafx.scene.control.Button addPlayButton()
